# Founding Software Engineer — AI Healthcare Platform

**Company:** NirogiAI (Private) Ltd  
**Location:** Colombo, Sri Lanka — Hybrid preferred; Remote within Sri Lanka considered  
**Type:** Full-time · Founding Role · Equity-bearing

---

> *"You will own systems, make architectural decisions, and ship real infrastructure."*

---

## About NirogiAI

NirogiAI is building a cloud-native, AI-enabled healthcare platform that connects patients, diagnostic providers, and specialist physicians through intelligent workflows and secure medical data systems.

This is a **founding engineering role**. You will work directly with the founders to build a production-grade system from the ground up. This is not a maintenance role and not a narrow feature role.

We are not looking for generalists with shallow exposure. We are looking for engineers with strong fundamentals and real system-building experience.

---

## What You'll Work On

You will design and build core components of the platform, including:

- **Backend services** using Python (FastAPI)
- **Linux-based** system deployment and debugging
- **Cloud infrastructure** and service deployment (GCP / AWS / Azure)
- **AI/LLM pipelines** including Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
- **Secure ingestion and processing** of medical data (documents, imaging, structured data)
- **Event-driven systems** and asynchronous processing pipelines
- **Production monitoring**, logging, and system reliability

